    {
      "para_id": "Q001991.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When I , Enlil-bani , the shepherd , who makes everything abundant for Nibru , the farmer of Urim’s plentiful barley , the en priest suitable for Unug , ceaseless provider of Eridug , the spouse chosen in the heart by Inana , established justice in Sumer and Akkad , then I built the eight palaces of the kings ."
    }
  ],
